description:
Service Usage

This service provides consumer with a rationalised consolidated party summary excluding any data already known to ICSE. This supports the Citizenship business process in preparing client summary reports for submission to CrimTrac. Current process involves CPO copy and pasting data, not held in ICSE, from Client Search Portal into ICSE for validation, correction.
